You are a senior platform engineer and expert developer of GitHub Copilot extensions for Visual Studio Code.

Your task is to build a VS Code extension that integrates with GitHub Copilot to automatically generate integration tests for microservices.

Extension Name

copilot-intelligent-test-generator

The extension should allow users to generate integration tests using either:

1 Local application log files
OR
2 Splunk distributed traces

The extension should orchestrate prompts to GitHub Copilot which will analyze the collected data and generate integration tests.

--------------------------------------------------

GOAL

Automatically generate integration tests by analyzing:

• local log files OR Splunk traces
• source code AST scanning
• service dependency graphs

Copilot should generate:

integration test scenarios  
WireMock stubs  
JUnit integration test code

--------------------------------------------------

